title: After state sync node stopped following the chain and unable to restore after restart.
body:
**Describe the bug**
Discord issue.
When user synced DB, had a lot of "Discovered new block" messages but none of "processed" or "Downloaded". 
When after few days noticed, restarted node and saw a lot of nodes to be done but progess is frozen - no following restarts help.

One of the root causes may be that User first had Nethermind synced on PC, then moved to geth and then came back to nethermind with different DB and new version.

**Expected behavior**
A clear and concise description of what you expected to happen.

**Screenshots**
If applicable, add screenshots to help explain your problem.

**Desktop (please complete the following information):**
 - Windows Server 19
 - Nethermind 1.14.1
